 Feature Selection vs. Hypothesis Selection<body>

  Feature Selection vs. Hypothesis Selection  
      Feature Selection- Prior knowledge selects relevant features, induction algorithm on relevant feature selects hypothesisesis Selection- Prior knowledge selects hypothesis as in explanation-based learning
 
 
WetSpring ?  DrySummer ? FireInFall
  A ??WetSpring
 B???C ?  DrySummmer
  A ? (B???C) ?  FireInFall and  
 C ? (B ??A)  ?  FireInFall share same features but only
 A ? (B???C) ?  FireInFall is logically consistent      
 
